    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Suggestion:\r\n- Remove any `verifySignatures` argument\r\n- Add a new `ProcessBlockHeaderNoVerifySig` method for the rare cases that you need to skip verification. \r\n- Abstract the code to be reusable between the two methods.\r\n\r\nWe are mostly concerned about accidental misuse of the method. \r\nA verbose API would help clarify / catch misuse. ",
